│                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ The function assumes that if `C` (the constant 127) is not poison, then the transformation is safe. But it fails to consider that the comparison operation       │
│ itself might produce poison due to the `samesign` predicate, independent of the constant operand.                                                                │
